        .tool-content
          section#features.tool-content__section 
            h2 GPT-3 Playground Features
            p Upword simplifies content creation by offering a centralized location for the entire workflow, from idea to publishing. Its all-in-one solution streamlines the process, reducing errors and delays. With a user-friendly interface and comprehensive features, Upword maximizes productivity and efficiency. Optimize your content workflow today with Upword.
            ul.tool-features 
              li.tool-features__item Add comments, both your own and those created by AI;
              li.tool-features__item Attach links and media files;
              li.tool-features__item Highlight what's important - Artificial Intelligence can help with this, too;
              li.tool-features__item Simplify complex and translate foreign texts;
              li.tool-features__item Listen to finished excerpts using the built-in audio tools.
          section#how-to.tool-content__section 
            h2 How to use GPT-3 Playground
            p The process of working with Upword is simple and intuitive. The platform has a web version, but it is more convenient to use the extension for Google Chrome.
            p It can be found in the official Google Store. In order to start using the tool, all you have to do is open the article you want to cut and run the extension.
            h3 Buy the product
