          section#target.tool-content__section
            h2 Who is best fit for GPT-3 Playground
            p  The tool will be useful to everyone who works with texts - not necessarily at a professional level. AI saves time - it makes it easier to follow the news, shorten articles from any source, and listen to finished material on the go.
            h3 Upword themselves identify the following categories of users who will benefit from their AI:
            ul
              li Students. Summarize a book, a research paper, a report - few students can say they don't have enough reading;
              li Entrepreneurs. AI will help businessmen not to lose time in searching for important information for them. Squeeze out current news, reports, business research-anything to keep up with changes in the workplace;
              li Marketers, advertisers, content managers. Write a blog post, make a progress report, or cut a lengthy online research, AI will be useful to anyone who works in media;
              li Executives, leads, managers. Often in a management job, you have to write a resume for management - with AI, this will be a quick and easy task. Upword features allow you to share finished reports and texts with the entire team.
          section#pricing.tool-content__section
            h2 GPT-3 Playground Pricing
            p The platform has a free trial period of 7 days and several paid subscription options:
            ul 
              li Monthly - this will cost $15;
              li Annual - the $150 price includes two free months.
            p Upword has a student discount of 66%. To get it, you have to prove that you are actually studying.
